Note: This chord is only from the second part of the song till the outro. I only transfer the chord from the already exist guitarpro tab. I just wanna to make it fun to play for beginners who love DT.
The chords are in synchronization of the key of it. Simple 6-string chord version.
The chords in this version are a bit easier to remember without killing the DT sound, an advice is to play the major chords like Rush would have done, you can find the shapes inside.
